# Private layout docs/drafts — the fork (bbmtab/PCAPdroid) is a PUBLIC repo.
# These work-in-progress UI specs (and the layout buildprint image) stay
# local; do not commit/upload them. The *_v2 drafts below are untracked; the
# v1 names were previously committed and have been `git rm --cached`'d
# (kept in history, recoverable via git log) — listing them here prevents
# them from being re-added.
UNIFIED_UI_ARCHITECTURE.md
protection_layout.md
protection_layout_v2.md
Network_layout_tab.md
Network_layout_tab_v2.md
app_managemen_tab_layout_blueprint.md
app_managemen_tab_layout_blueprint_v2.md
firewall_blocking_tab.md
icon_bluprint.md
filter_list_plan.md
blocklist layout.md
block_list-Layout_buildprint.jpeg

# Private infra / CI-debug scratch — never upload to the public repo.
#   "ssh admin@10.148.0.2" leaks an internal host in its filename.
#   curl.exe / *.log / logcat-e2e-* are run artifacts downloaded during CI triage.
ssh admin@*
curl.exe
job_log.txt
job_log_full.txt
logcat-e2e-*.txt
run_*.log
e2e-logcat/
/*claudeci*.json
